❄️ FrostIQ
FrostIQ is a smart authentication and verification system designed for modern web and mobile apps. It leverages FastAPI for lightning-fast backend APIs and Twilio for secure OTP-based user login, offering a seamless and secure onboarding experience.

✨ Features
🔐 OTP-based Authentication via SMS (Twilio)
⚡ Built with FastAPI – fast, asynchronous Python web framework
📱 Easy integration with mobile or web frontends
🧪 Interactive API docs using Swagger and ReDoc
🌍 Ready for cloud deployment
--
